This is the README file for the Dragon/Write package by James Howard
<howardjp@dragon.ham.muohio.edu>.  This package includes enhanced versions
of write(1), mesg(1), and writed(8).  This software has only been tested 
with the Linux operating system, however, it should port to similar
operating systems with little trouble.

			To compile  --  make all
			To install  --  make install (you must be "root")

To download the latest version of the Dragon/Write package, go to
dragon.ham.muohio.edu:/pub/howardjp/write.  The current version number is
0.0.1.
